WEBVTT

1
00:36:44.890 --> 00:36:47.560 
不  合情合理
Well, no, it makes perfect sense.

2
00:36:48.110 --> 00:36:51.400 
我三年级时  人人都以为我疯了...
In third grade, everyone said I was crazy, but I knew our teacher...

3
00:36:51.610 --> 00:36:53.860 
...但我知道老师  一定是金星来的
...had to be from Venus or something.

4
00:36:54.070 --> 00:36:56.820 
魏太太其实来自木星的...
Ms. Edelson. Jupiter, actually. Well, one of the moons.

5
00:36:58.240 --> 00:36:59.120 
其中之一月球
...revolve.

6
00:36:59.370 --> 00:37:00.700 
各位...
Class...

7
00:37:01.160 --> 00:37:03.540 
...安静并请注意!
...be quiet and pay attention!

8
00:37:04.500 --> 00:37:06.120 
若我要再
If I have to tell you...

9
00:37:06.330 --> 00:37:08.710 
说一次...
...one more time...

10
00:37:10.420 --> 00:37:11.630 
穿上吧
Let's put it on.

11
00:37:12.460 --> 00:37:13.300 
穿什么?
Put what on?

12
00:37:13.920 --> 00:37:16.430 
你穿的最后一套衣服
The last suit you'll ever wear.

